just a stupid gui wrapper around portablemc.
for <serious gaming> you should probably use portablemc.

build dependencies:
  - python3
  - pip install pyinstaller portablemc tkinter sv-ttk

build windows version:
  $ make all

get a pre-built executable:
  - windows:      https://pub.krzysckh.org/pmc-gui.exe
  - x86_64-linux: https://pub.krzysckh.org/pmc-gui-linux-x86-64

version can be one of:
  - optifine:newest
  - optifine:version.name.number (e.g. optifine:1.12.2 or optifine:1.19)
  - newest
  - version.name.number (e.g. 1.8.8 or 1.12)
